    "description": "Based on a character from Rimsky-Korsakov's opera The Tale of Tsar Saltan, the painting captures the moment of magical transformation between woman and swan. The iridescent whites and blues of the feathered costume shimmer against a darkening sky, creating an atmosphere of enchantment.",
