    "dimensions": "160 cm × 177 cm",
    "location": "Tretyakov Gallery, Moscow",
    "description": "A mysterious female figure emerges from an overwhelming mass of lilac blossoms, her form barely distinguishable from the dense, jewel-toned foliage. Vrubel's thick, mosaic-like application of paint transforms the botanical subject into a vision of nature's intoxicating, almost threatening beauty.",
